race.comment: KIM'S A REBEL (7) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fourth (25.18) from Box 8 at Goulburn over 440m. Goes very well from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Can bounce back. ON THE RAZZLE (8) latest effort finished 4th in a Grade 5 on November 8 over 520m at this track behind American Indian beaten 5.5 lengths (30.48). Can feature in the finish. ZIPPING BOP (5) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 5th (30.33) at this track. One of the main contenders. RUSTY CORTEZ (4) will give backers a sight.
